      <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>In an emergency contact the Police on 999. If you think there has been a crime but it is not an emergency, call 101.</p>
<p>Contact Adult Social Care on:</p>
<ul>
<li>Reading 0118 937 3747 </li>
<li>West Berkshire 01635 519056 </li>
<li>Wokingham 0118 974 6800</li>
<li>Out of normal working hours, contact the Emergency Duty Team 01344 786 543.</li>
</ul>
<p>Each Council has its own web pages and information leaflets. If you require the information in a different format or in easy read, please ask.</p>
