        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Reading</strong> - call 0118 937 3747 or email <a href="mailto:safeguarding.adults@reading.gov.uk">safeguarding.adults@reading.gov.uk</a></p>
<p><strong>West Berkshire</strong> - call 01635 519056 or email <a href="mailto:safeguardingadults@westberks.gov.uk">safeguardingadults@westberks.gov.uk</a></p>
