<h2>Audit Tool Templates and Care Governance Protocol</h2>
<p>Templates and guidance for staff to use when carrying out audits: </p>
<p><strong><a href="/media/1194/west-berkshire-safeguarding-adults-audit-framework.docx" target="_blank" title="Multi Agency Audit Framework Strategy">Multi-agency Audit Framework Strategy,</a></strong> <a href="/media/1172/adult-safeguarding-audit-tool-template.docx" target="_blank" title="Audit Tool Template"></a></p>
